# CODEOWNERS for hklug-sitegen
#
# GitHub Copilot reviews code changes automatically.
# Article files in data/news/ have no owner, so article-only PRs
# will NOT trigger a Copilot review request.
#
# To fully enable conditional reviews:
# Go to Settings → Code and automation → Code review →
# set Copilot to "Only when requested via CODEOWNERS".

/bin/       @github-copilot[bot]
/lib/       @github-copilot[bot]
/template/  @github-copilot[bot]
/t/         @github-copilot[bot]
/.github/   @github-copilot[bot]
*.pl        @github-copilot[bot]
*.pm        @github-copilot[bot]
*.yaml      @github-copilot[bot]
*.yml       @github-copilot[bot]
